---
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>

    <script is:inline>
      const theme = (() => {
        if (typeof localStorage !== 'undefined' && localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
          return localStorage.getItem('theme');
        }
        if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches) {
          return 'dark';
        }
        return 'light';
      })();
      if (theme === 'dark') {
        document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
      } else {
        document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
      }
      window.localStorage.setItem('theme', theme);
    </script>

    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script is:inline async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-DC032Y6PFZ"></script>
    <script is:inline>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());

      gtag('config', 'G-DC032Y6PFZ');
    </script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <title>About Us - 16-0 Play</title>
    <meta name="description" content="About 16-0play. Discover the story behind the ultimate cricket team building and season simulation game." />
  
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script is:inline async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3180090639225904" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-[var(--color-canvas-soft)] text-[var(--color-ink)] selection:bg-yellow-500/30">
    <NavBar client:load />
    <div class="pt-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--color-ink)]">About Us</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--color-body)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Welcome to <strong>16-0play</strong>, your number one source for the ultimate cricket strategy and simulation experience.</p>
        <p>Founded by passionate cricket fans and gaming enthusiasts, 16-0play was born out of a desire to create the most engaging, challenging, and realistic cricket team management game on the web.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] mt-8">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to provide cricket lovers worldwide with a platform to test their tactical acumen. We believe that managing a cricket team requires more than just picking star players—it demands strategy, balance, and foresight. We aim to capture that essence in every simulation we run, allowing users to experience the thrill of chasing a perfect 16-0 season.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] mt-8">What We Offer</h2>
        <p>We offer a deep, statistics-driven simulation engine where you can draft legendary players, build your ultimate playing XI, and compete on a global leaderboard. We constantly update our platform with the latest features, inspired by real-world cricket tournaments like the IPL.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] mt-8">Join the Community</h2>
        <p>Whether you're here to casually simulate a few matches or relentlessly pursue the 16-0 perfect season, we are thrilled to have you as part of our community. Thank you for choosing 16-0play.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[var(--color-ink)] hover:text-yellow-600 font-semibold transition-colors">
          &larr; Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>
